  "detailed_description": "You are a Taoist from the Heavenly Master's Mansion, and your master sent you down the mountain to experience. You will see various ancient Chinese monsters, fairies, and Buddhas, fighting or trading with them to obtain various weapons, elixirs, and spiritual treasures. Cultivate various Taoist spells to drive out monsters:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/568660820bcb4b3d7bd75edca2c5e6ef.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/506b5e2dba53c0b3a31dbc3d1669e815.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span>Faced with the dilemma of limited financial resources, you need to understand various ways to make money and understand the seasonal cultivation of crops:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/5116203197f5846349b5e4d23ede992a.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Personally hunting or cultivating animal companions for hunting: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/d4685dfa1330b7d3e16c1c672631e387.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Raising Poultry and Livestock:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/5f97dbf8fd18673caa0bee63e7ec3d91.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Fishing, chopping trees, and cooking:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/4d92fc9c9af82c6b4988ef219fa892b0.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Alchemy and pharmaceuticals:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/2a8bab3159095dbadccd032d64518134.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Stir frying tea and brewing:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/f9b8223c82ecb6a50484720c2f8c3cc5.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Even crafting various weapons. Do your best to live.",
  "about_the_game": "You are a Taoist from the Heavenly Master's Mansion, and your master sent you down the mountain to experience. You will see various ancient Chinese monsters, fairies, and Buddhas, fighting or trading with them to obtain various weapons, elixirs, and spiritual treasures. Cultivate various Taoist spells to drive out monsters:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/568660820bcb4b3d7bd75edca2c5e6ef.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/506b5e2dba53c0b3a31dbc3d1669e815.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span>Faced with the dilemma of limited financial resources, you need to understand various ways to make money and understand the seasonal cultivation of crops:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/5116203197f5846349b5e4d23ede992a.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Personally hunting or cultivating animal companions for hunting: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/d4685dfa1330b7d3e16c1c672631e387.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Raising Poultry and Livestock:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/5f97dbf8fd18673caa0bee63e7ec3d91.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Fishing, chopping trees, and cooking:<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987010/extras/4d92fc9c9af82c6b4988ef219fa892b0.avif?t=1720409385\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Alchemy and pharmaceuticals:<spa